      "content": "WHOIS for missallanahstarr.com shows registrant email lugai665@163.com (Chinese NetEase provider) with fabricated Japanese address listing contradictory prefectures (Kyoto, Saitama). Domain updated 2026-04-15, one day before campaign launch. Registration via PacificDomains, LLC.",
